  "title": "Draftsman (3D AutoCAD) - North - WCDT",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Job Scopes：</strong></em></p><ul><li>Create 2D and 3D drawings for AV system layouts and equipment placement.</li><li><p>Prepare floor plans, wiring diagrams, and rack layout drawing.</p></li><li><p>Work with project engineers to understand project requirements.</p></li><li><p>Update drawings based on revisions and site measurements.</p></li><li><p>Produce shop drawings and as-built drawings for project handover.</p></li><li><p>Ensure drawings follow project standards and specifications.</p></li><li><p>Support site teams with drawing updates and clarifications.</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper documentation and drawing files.<br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br />Wecruit Pte Ltd | 20C0270<br />Tew Jie Wei | R22106822</p></li></ul>",
